    "more": "<p><strong>OpenAlex Domain, Fields and Subfields</strong></p><p><a href='images/Logo YUFE-General.png' target='_blank' rel='noopener'><img src='images/Logo YUFE-General.png' alt='Logo YUFE' style='max-width:100%;height:auto;'></a></p>",
    "intro": "\u003cp\u003e  \nThis interactive graph represents the hierarchical structure of research interests in \n\u003cstrong\u003ePhysical Sciences\u003c/strong\u003e extracted from a set of responses to the YUFE Task 5.3 survey, the 3 levels displayed are: \n\u003cul\u003e  \n  \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style\u003d"color:#24EB84;"\u003eDomain\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e  \n  \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style\u003d"color:#EB3424;"\u003eField\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e  \n  \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style\u003d"color:#2563EB;"\u003eSubfield\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\nThe size of each node is proportional to the number of mentions (\u003cem\u003eWeight\u003c/em\u003e) received from the participants in the survey. \nUse the search box or the group selector to focus on specific areas. \n\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003e3 levels\u003c/strong\u003e:\n\u003cdiv style\u003d"display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:6px;"\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d"/yufe5.3/network_PhysicalSciences_2/images/OPENALEX_1.jpg" target\u003d"_blank" rel\u003d"noopener"\u003e\u003cimg src\u003d"/yufe5.3/network_PhysicalSciences_2/images/OPENALEX_1.jpg" alt\u003d"OPENALEX 1" style\u003d"height:80px; border:1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius:4px;"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d"/yufe5.3/network_PhysicalSciences_2/images/OPENALEX_2.jpg" target\u003d"_blank" rel\u003d"noopener"\u003e\u003cimg src\u003d"/yufe5.3/network_PhysicalSciences_2/images/OPENALEX_2.jpg" alt\u003d"OPENALEX 2" style\u003d"height:80px; border:1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius:4px;"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d"/yufe5.3/network_PhysicalSciences_2/images/OPENALEX_3.jpg" target\u003d"_blank" rel\u003d"noopener"\u003e\u003cimg src\u003d"/yufe5.3/network_PhysicalSciences_2/images/OPENALEX_3.jpg" alt\u003d"OPENALEX 3" style\u003d"height:80px; border:1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius:4px;"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/p\u003e ",
